      "narration_keys": ["opening_clarity", "judgement_default", "warning_default"],
      "notes": "Branching decision rule. It favors lower-ambiguity, lower-risk choices when multiple routes appear."
    },
    {
      "id": "rule_low_supply_keep_distance",
      "name": "Under scarcity, do not reach for the gleaming thing",
